TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(-7,-2,1);
$b = random(4,10,1);
$c = random(2,4,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));

Evaluate the definite integral:
$BR
$PAR
   \( \displaystyle{ \int_{$a}^{0} \sqrt{$b - $c x} \,dx} = \)
   \{ans_rule(35) \}
$BR
$BR

EOT

$ans = (2/(3*$c))*(($b - $a*$c)**(3/2) - $b**(3/2));
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

